summary: An ordinance accepting a bill of sale, dated the 29th day of April, 1929; Copy of Resolution No. 3195 of the County Commissioners of King County, Washington, dated the 15th day of April, 1929, and Certificate of the Seattle Title Trust Company, dated the 29th day of April, 1929, filed with the City of Seattle by the Pacific Northwest Traction Company, pursuant to the provisions of Ordinance No. 56720.
